Diffbot-Article

This is an unofficial module for diffbot article api. It supports both the Get and Post methods and are used as follows

	use Diffbot::Article;
        
        my $json_obj = articleGet((url => $url, token => $token, fields => \@fieldarrayref, version => $version))
        my $json_obj = articlePost((url => $url, token => $token, fields => \@fieldsarrayref, srcfile => $srcfile, content_type => $content_type, version => $version, data => $data))

Also view the two examples included to see how the two methods are being used.

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

	perl Makefile.PL
	make && make install

SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

After installing, you can find detail documentation for this module with the
perldoc command or try the man command also

    	perldoc Diffbot::Article
    	man Diffbot::Article

